From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: WilyWork <hezodions@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 15:54:15 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] Add growable plant abstraction

Introduce PandaGrowablePlant to expose shared helpers for reading a plant's growth state, current growth level, and maximum growth level.

Implement the contract for vanilla age-based plants and retain the configured BlockStateInteger upper bound for callers.

